		<title>Episode 032: In Search of the Soul, Part 4</title>
		<link>http://www.beretta-online.com/wordpress/2010/episode-032-in-search-of-the-soul-part-4/</link>
		<comments>http://www.beretta-online.com/wordpress/2010/episode-032-in-search-of-the-soul-part-4/#comments</comments>
